								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the organisation within the BBC.  For the television channel, see <a href="BBC_News_(TV_channel)" title="BBC News (TV channel)">BBC News (TV channel)</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="BBC_News_(disambiguation)" title="BBC News (disambiguation)">BBC News (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
